de.slackspace.openkeepass.domain

Class KeePassFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.slackspace.openkeepass.domain.KeePassFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KeePassFileElement

    public class KeePassFile
extends java.lang.Object
implements KeePassFileElement
    A KeePassFile represents the structure of a KeePass database. This is the central entry point to read data from the KeePass database.

      • getEntriesByTitle

        public java.util.List<Entry> getEntriesByTitle(java.lang.String title,
                                               boolean matchExactly)
        Retrieves a list of entries with matching titles.

        If the matchExactly flag is true, only entries which have an exactly matching title will be returned, otherwise all entries which contain the given title will be returned.

        Parameters:
        title - the title which should be searched
        matchExactly - if true only entries which have an exactly matching title will be returned
        Returns:
        a list of entries with matching titles
        See Also:
